Interface IDisplayObject

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IHiddenDisplayObject, IMultiSelectDisplayObject, IReadOnlyDisplayObject, IRedirectDisplayObject, ISingleSelectDisplayObject, ITextDisplayObject, ITextNoEchoDisplayObject, IVerifyTextNoEchoDisplayObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HiddenDisplayObject, MultiSelectDisplayObject, ReadOnlyDisplayObject, RedirectDisplayObject, SingleSelectDisplayObject, TextDisplayObject, TextNoEchoDisplayObject, VerifyTextNoEchoDisplayObject

    public interface IDisplayObject
    Defines the common interface for implementing an IBM Cognos display object. Display objects are used for generating forms when prompting the user.
